---
title: Carb Smart Summer Steak Salad with Nectarines and Strawberry Balsamic Vinaigrette
description: The intense flavours from the strawberry balsamic vinaigrette alone will have you drooling over this plate! Spooned over steak and greens with some feta and pepitas and you're good to go!

